==Arabic alphabet==

===Letter===
'''{{ARchar|ز / ‍ز}}''' (zāyn)

# The eleventh letter of the [[Arabic]] alphabet. It is preceded by {{ARchar|[[ر]]}} and followed by {{ARchar|[[س]]}}.
# The seventh letter in traditional [[abjad]] order, which is used in place of numerals for list numbering ([[abjad numerals]]). It is preceded by {{ARchar|[[و]]}} and followed by {{ARchar|[[ح]]}}.

